38583.name: Numeracy (total) (Baten 2015)
38583.description: Numeracy estimates (ABCC) by birth decade and country, both before and after 1800. Use "age heaping"; that is, where age data frequently displays excess frequencies at attractive numbers, e.g. multiples of five, to measure cognitive ability in quantitative reasoning.
